            "content": "<p>At The Promise Ring Co. we are committed to providing you with exceptional service and ensuring that your purchase of your ring is a truly special and sentimental experience. We understand that these pieces aren't just jewellery; they are symbols of love, commitment, and cherished moments. </p><p>That's why we stand by our products and offer a 5-year guarantee to give you peace of mind*</p>"
