            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<h2>repair & replace</h2><p>Our 5-year guarantee covers the following:</p><p><strong>Repair:</strong> If your jewellery shows a clear manufacturing fault, we will repair it free of charge within the first 5 years from the date of purchase</p><p><strong>Replacement: </strong>If, in rare cases, we are unable to repair your jewellery, we will provide you with an entirely new, identical ring for a small fee. If we do not stock your style, we will work with you to find a close alternative</p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_style": "solid"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_3FkyiW": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/9_c0662fe6-e990-44c8-9dce-014fe56f6b64.png",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "exclusions",
            "content": "<p>Please note that our guarantee does not cover damages or defects resulting from:</p><p><em>Normal wear and tear, or fading of plating</em></p><p><em><strong>Accidental damage, including but not limited to scratches, dents, or bent rings</strong></em></p><p><em>Unauthorised modifications or repairs performed by third parties</em></p><p><em><strong>Damage caused by misuse, neglect, or improper care</strong></em></p><p><em>The warranty only applies to the size and style of the ring you originally purchased. Replacements in a different size or style are not covered under the warranty</em></p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_style": "solid"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_N4fA9W": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/10_e09b96b5-a075-4eff-864f-94f64621b677.png",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "requesting warranty coverage",
            "content": "<p>If you believe your jewellery has a manufacturing fault and is covered under our guarantee, please follow these steps:</p><p>Contact our Customer Service: <a href=\"mailto:info@thepromiseringco.com\">info@thepromise</a><a href=\"mailto:info@thepromiseringco.com\">co.com</a> to initiate the warranty claim</p><p>Provide your original order information, including the order number and date of purchase</p><p>Describe the issue with your jewellery and provide clear photographs if possible</p><p>Our Customer Service team will guide you through the process of returning your item for assessment</p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_style": "solid"
          }
        }
